Vol / Page: 2
Edition:
Quote: RETURNED SOLDIERS .. Establishing of Businesses. -The association asks that opportunity be given to suitable returned soldiers to establish themselves in business. In this, as in all other schemes, the keynote is the suitability of the individual. It is considered that this is the natural complement of the land settlement scheme at present in operation.
